query_preview:
The bug occurs when using a double slash in the external location path for Glue & S3 connectors in Hive connector. The table is created with location 's3://bucket/foo//bar' but returns empty results when queried, while Delta and Iceberg connectors work correctly. This suggests an issue with path handling or file resolution when double slashes are present in S3 paths. s3://bucket/foo//bar external_location create table insert into table query create table test_slash (c1 int) with (external_location = 's3://bucket/foo//bar');
insert into test_slash values (1);
table test_slash;

